      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.502-1</ph> Requirements for setting	aside acquisitions.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1159e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1188e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall	set aside an individual acquisition or class of acquisitions for	competition among small businesses when-</p>
               <ol id="d1159e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1188e16" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                It is determined	to be in the interest of maintaining or mobilizing the Nation’s	full productive capacity, war or national defense programs; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1188e21" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Assuring	that a fair proportion of Government contracts in each industry	is placed with small business concerns; and the circumstances described	in <xref href="19.502-2.dita#FAR_19_502_2"
                              base="i1100762"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.502-2</xref> or <xref href="19.502-3.dita#FAR_19_502_3"
                              base="i1100796"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.502-3</xref>(a) exist.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1188e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The requirement in paragraph	(a) of this section does not apply to purchases at or below the	micro-purchase threshold, or purchases from required sources under <xref href="Part_8.dita#FAR_Part_8"
                        base="i1118293"
                        outputclass="fm:Part"
                        class="- topic/xref ">part  8</xref>(e.g., Committee	for Purchase From People Who are Blind or Severely Disabled).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
